name: Navy on White
description: Navy inner layer with White and Navy houndstooth outer layer fabric flower, attached to plastic handband with matching Houndstooth fabric. Can be made into a clip(aligator), headband(stretchy elastic) or a pin. Please send an email to gardenstatehair@yahoo.com stating which way you'd like your hair accessory to be made after you place your order. NOTE: If NO EMAIL is sent, all hair accessories for that specific order will be made into clips.
